{"tid":2102350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<党安法>法國號召歐盟反擊中國","createTime":"2020-07-10T11:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T14:56:46.000Z","uid":227801,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"32f1e32e20c6cc42494502d6d7858e040549df84","tid":2102350,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:44:05.000Z","msg":"係咪同德國爭歐盟領導地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/7038721/article-%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%96%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E8%99%9F%E5%8F%AC%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E5%8F%8D%E6%93%8A/?ismobile=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F7038721%2Farticle-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25A6%2596%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2599%259F%25E5%258F%25AC%25E6%25AD%2590%25E7%259B%259F%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2593%258A%2F%3Fismobile%3Dtrue&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumlznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=d06ed3e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/7038721/article-%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%96%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A-%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E8%99%9F%E5%8F%AC%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E5%8F%8D%E6%93%8A/?ismobile=true</a><br />\n法國外長勒德里安（Jean-Yves Le Drian）前天表明，不會對北京的香港政策「無動於衷」。儘管北京昨天警告法國無權干涉中國內政，勒德里安偕同西班牙外長召開聯合記者會時仍強調，將協同歐盟各國採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n勒德里安昨天在參議院外交事務委員會中表示，法國不會對香港國家安全法問題袖手旁觀，「我們會在適當時機採取行動」，並強調將與其他歐洲國家協調合作。<br />\n面對勒德里安的發言，中國外交部發言人趙立堅昨天回應：「香港事務純屬中國內政，任何外國無權干涉。」北京也強調希望「有關國家」能「謹言慎行，多做有利於香港繁榮穩定的事」。<br />\n然而昨天勒德里安與西班牙外長龔薩雷茲（Arancha Gonzalez Laya）在巴黎外交部前召開聯合記者會時，勒德里安再次重申對香港政策的態度：「在我們看來，國安法嚴重撼動了1997年的基本法，以及『一國兩制』原則下的香港自治。」<br />\n他說，旅港法人也可能成為新措施的受害者，他們將於20日的歐盟外長會議上討論這個問題。<br />\n相較於美國與英國的強硬態度，歐盟目前對此顯得過於保守。歐盟日前呼籲中國「避免所有損害香港自治的行動」，但除此之外，尚未採取任何反擊措施。"},{"pid":"66665afd880ac380f7d89a93d03c7681f9b87c85","tid":2102350,"uid":304695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:47:06.000Z","msg":"法國! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6bd13fd841c0bd7ac914c9a7d6611dbef71ce1","tid":2102350,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T11:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821b0606e727a7ae7c2d0b1bdca88cb3cdbabc9c","tid":2102350,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T13:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3dc5c1f314806659aae2fc7630830f29dbb1481","tid":2102350,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T14:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hDy3emH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhDy3emH.jpg&h=ffff381d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}